Appendix F: Numerical Toy Model ‚Äî Jupyter/Python (ADDED)

Goal. Integrate the bounce with radiation (w = 1/3) in natural units 8œÄG/3 = 1.

Equations.
œÅ(a) = œÅ_Œ© (a_min/a)^4,
H(a) = ¬± ‚àö[ œÅ(a) (1 - œÅ(a)/œÅ_Œ©) ],
